The mischievous '''faerie dragons''' came from a branch of the [[dragon]] [[Proto-dragon/Evolutionary tree|family tree]], closely related to [[pseudodragon]]s. They were intelligent and capable of using language.

{{quote|''Faerie dragons. This will be aggravating.''|[[Dorn]] the [[Blackguard]]}}
